title: Google\Cloud\SecurityCenter\V1\ListBigQueryExportsRequest
name: ListBigQueryExportsRequest
description:
Request message for listing BigQuery exports at a given scope e.g.

organization, folder or project.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.securitycenter.v1.ListBigQueryExportsRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The parent, which owns the collection of BigQuery exports. Its format is "organizations/[organization_id]", "folders/[folder_id]", "projects/[project_id]".

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The maximum number of configs to return. The service may return fewer than this value. If unspecified, at most 10 configs will be returned. The maximum value is 1000; values above 1000 will be coerced to 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: A page token, received from a previous ListBigQueryExports call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to ListBigQueryExports must match the call that provided the page token.
